<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 09:12:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>经合组织上调全球增长前景 美国表现优于其他国家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/oecd-upgrades-global-growth-outlook-us-outperforms-2024-05-02/</link><description>经合组织周四表示，由于美国经济活动富有弹性，全球经济增长速度快于几个月前的预期，而通胀与央行目标的融合速度也快于预期，并上调了展望。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 07:05:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/oecd-upgrades-global-growth-outlook-us-outperforms-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>安赛乐米塔尔仍预计今年钢铁需求增长3-4%（不包括中国）</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/arcelormittal-q1-profit-tops-expectations-2024-05-02/</link><description>全球第二大钢铁制造商安赛乐米塔尔周四重申，预计今年中国以外的全球钢铁需求将增长 3-4%，因为该公司公布的第一季度收益超出了分析师的预期。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 05:20:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/arcelormittal-q1-profit-tops-expectations-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国官员敦促中俄宣布只有人类而非人工智能控制核武器</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-official-urges-china-russia-declare-only-humans-not-ai-control-nuclear-2024-05-02/</link><description>周四，一名美国高级官员敦促中国和俄罗斯效仿美国和其他国家的声明，即只有人类而非人工智能才能做出部署核武器的决定。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 04:49:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-official-urges-china-russia-declare-only-humans-not-ai-control-nuclear-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>汇丰维持香港最优惠贷款利率于5.875%不变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-keeps-best-lending-rate-hong-kong-unchanged-5875-2024-05-02/</link><description>汇丰控股周四表示，在香港事实上的央行维持通过隔夜贴现窗口收取的基本利率不变，追随美联储维持利率稳定的决定后，该公司已将香港最优惠贷款利率维持在5.875%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 04:27:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-keeps-best-lending-rate-hong-kong-unchanged-5875-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>渣打银行利润超过手续费收入增长预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/standard-chartered-q1-profit-rises-55-beats-estimates-2024-05-02/</link><description>渣打银行周四第一季度税前利润超出预期，增长 5.5%，其交易和财富业务收入的激增足以弥补额外的信贷损失。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 04:24:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/standard-chartered-q1-profit-rises-55-beats-estimates-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾因南海争端召见中国外交官</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-summons-chinese-diplomat-over-south-china-sea-flare-up-2024-05-02/</link><description>菲律宾周四召见一名中国外交官，抗议北京在南海争议浅滩对菲律宾船只使用高压水枪，称其为骚扰和“危险举动”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 04:22:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-summons-chinese-diplomat-over-south-china-sea-flare-up-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>香港央行维持关键利率不变，追踪美联储决定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-central-bank-keeps-key-rate-unchanged-tracks-fed-move-2024-05-02/</link><description>香港金融管理局（金管局）周四将通过隔夜贴现窗口收取的基本利率维持在 5.75% 不变，以追随美联储维持利率稳定的决定。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 03:21:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-central-bank-keeps-key-rate-unchanged-tracks-fed-move-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体报道，中国南方道路塌陷已造成 36 人死亡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/road-collapse-southern-china-kills-36-reports-state-media-2024-05-02/</link><description>据官方媒体周四报道，中国广东省一高速公路路段塌陷导致车辆坠落，造成 36 人死亡、另外 30 人受伤，当时正值数百万人在该国度假期间出行。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 03:20:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/road-collapse-southern-china-kills-36-reports-state-media-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>台湾称参加世卫大会可能很难，布林肯表示支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-may-be-hard-attend-who-assembly-blinken-offers-support-2024-05-02/</link><description>在美国催促邀请后，台湾外交部长周四表示，台湾参加今年的世界卫生组织年会将很困难，希望更多国家支持其出席。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 02:32:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-may-be-hard-attend-who-assembly-blinken-offers-support-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>所罗门群岛选择对中国友好的马内莱为新总理</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-chooses-jeremiah-manele-new-prime-minister-2024-05-02/</link><description>周四，所罗门群岛立法者选举杰里米亚·马内莱(Jeremiah Manele)为新任总理，提升了这位前外交部长的地位，他承诺继续这个太平洋岛国的国际政策，拉近与中国的距离。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 01:39:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-chooses-jeremiah-manele-new-prime-minister-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>日元走软，疑似干预后大幅升幅回落</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-gives-up-ground-vs-dollar-following-surge-suspected-intervention-2024-05-02/</link><description>日元兑美元周四下跌，在周三晚些时候突然飙升后逆转方向，交易员和分析师很快将其归因于日本当局的干预。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 01:28:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-gives-up-ground-vs-dollar-following-surge-suspected-intervention-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>美联储信号安抚股市，日元再次波动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-05-02/</link><description>周四，在美联储驳斥了重返加息的言论后，世界市场弥漫着一种宽慰的感觉，而日元则在另一轮疑似一轮外汇干预后回落。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 00:23:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>拜登将中国、日本和印度的经济困境归咎于“仇外心理”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-blames-china-japan-indias-economic-woes-xenophobia-2024-05-02/</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登周三表示，从中国到日本和印度的“仇外心理”正在阻碍它们的增长，因为他认为移民对美国经济有利。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 00:06:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-blames-china-japan-indias-economic-woes-xenophobia-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：鲍威尔引发股市波动，日元飙升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-01/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 21:46:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>美国反兴奋剂机构猛烈抨击世界反兴奋剂机构在中国兴奋剂案中的“半真半假”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/usada-slams-wada-half-truths-china-doping-case-2024-05-01/</link><description>美国反兴奋剂机构（USADA）周三批评世界反兴奋剂机构（WADA）“半真半假”，此前该机构发布了一份概述其处理涉及中国游泳运动员案件的文件。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 20:02:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/usada-slams-wada-half-truths-china-doping-case-2024-05-01/</guid></item></channel></rss>